{"tid":1502784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到方法「生」抗爭資金","createTime":"2019-08-24T17:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T18:56:33.000Z","uid":32818,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0119d10259603ab7a64ec0d66d43f48f3d652b","tid":1502784,"uid":32818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"連燈仔同香港人 個個都上YouTube <br />\nYoutube有廣告分紅<br />\n搵個可靠名人 如議員/海外流亡義士（開左名）⋯⋯<br />\n開個channel 開埋廣告功能 片嘅內容乜都冇所謂<br />\n聽講愈長愈多廣告愈多收益？<br />\n我地個個一得閒就開個YouTube 分頁 loop<br />\nMute左佢 由佢自動播 播曬廣告唔好skip<br />\n每個月嘅收入就開誠布公 出番個清晰報告<br />\n資金就用嚟幫義士<br />\n依個方法可以唔洗大家直接出錢 又幫到資金問題<br />\n學生都幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有其他平台都有分紅嘅都可以做<br />\n以前有見過話係Spotify放冇聲嘅「歌」狂loop都有錢收<br />\n未知細節是否可以 希望集思廣義<br />\n認同請幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ae19d180ad6eb34e57338968acaac9069a73d8fa","tid":1502784,"uid":32818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901c68beb43018bf733de8ee98f9c987e2d4f18a","tid":1502784,"uid":32818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"生金蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e1da945342a3213efc7545e6d663d0a95466ee","tid":1502784,"uid":309585,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"YouTube 一定封啦"},{"pid":"c7a6b416e87bd56090f1fda22faf1c0316cacb97","tid":1502784,"uid":32818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65e1da945342a3213efc7545e6d663d0a95466ee","tid":1502784,"uid":309585,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"YouTube 一定封啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"何解？內容冇所謂係指好似d垃圾Channel咁 圖加字<br />\n每張幾十秒 加埋十分鐘就當片咁<br />\n有人睇 又唔係係內容